### Variables
@baseUrl = https://qjfygjtondljywhbqbfj.supabase.co/functions/v1
@authToken = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Test 1 - Réserver un lieu (cas nominal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/venues-reserve-venue
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "event_id": "event-uuid-here",
  "venue_id": "venue-uuid-here",
  "date": "2024-12-25T18:00:00Z"
}

### Test 2 - Erreur: event_id manquant
POST {{baseUrl}}/venues-reserve-venue
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "venue_id": "venue-uuid-here",
  "date": "2024-12-25T18:00:00Z"
}

